close_reason: pm governance hierarchy and strict core validation are complete for the release-readiness work.
body: "Governance expectations:\n- The release work is traceable from a parent epic to each release-readiness concern.\n- Each item has owner, reviewer, risk, confidence, sprint, release, files/docs/tests, and acceptance criteria.\n- Items are closed only after the related evidence exists.\n- pm validate is run at the end and warnings are reviewed."
